import React from 'react'
import {Component,Paper,Typography,Avatar} from '@material-ui/core'
import {LockOutlinedIcon} from '@material-ui/icons/LockOutlined'
import useClasses from './styles.js'

const Auth = () => {
  classes=useClasses()
  
  return (
   <Component component='main' maxWidth='xs'>
     <Paper className={classes.paper} elevation={3}>

     </Paper>
   </Component> 
  )
}

export default Auth
